<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reschedule Request</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ff9800;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #333;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ff9800;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #f57c00;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #ff9800;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">Reschedule Required</div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>
          We regret to inform you that your scheduled session cannot take place at the originally planned time because your mentor is currently unavailable.
        </p>
        <p>
          But no worries! You can now choose a new time slot that works best for you.
        </p>
        <p>
          Please visit the <strong>Reschedule Meeting</strong> section on the booking page to select a new available slot.
        </p>
        <p>Once selected, your meeting will be automatically rescheduled for that time.</p>
        <a href="<%= bookingPageUrl %>" class="btn">Reschedule Now</a>
        <p>If you need assistance or have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Need help? <a href="mailto:support@example.com">Contact our support team</a>.
        </p>
        <p>We appreciate your understanding and flexibility!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
